h the required GraalVM\",\"completed\":true},{\"text\":\"Patch reachability metadata for the missing registrations without overwriting existing local edits\",\"completed\":true},{\"text\":\"Re-run the targeted Gradle test until it passes with the same GraalVM\",\"completed\":true}]}}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
